I love all these three aspects, couldn’t let go of two to focus on only one, but at the same time can’t have my page looking messy. Hence came up with this. I’m glad you like it. ❤️

@the_chill_n_chew totally get you! If you scroll through mine too, it’s gone through a bunch of changes haha. Sometimes I think about whether I should focus on one thing to get better, but I also am the type of person who likes working on multiple things, and if I focus on one that’s just not me. Even if it puts me at a disadvantage (both skill and ig wise), I’d rather have it be more representative of me :)
